data.description: Welcome home! This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a true gem, offering a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and versatility. Situated on a spacious flat lot, this property boasts a range of features that make it the perfect place for you and your family to call home. With three spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms, everyone can have their own privacy. You will also appreciate the inviting covered front porch, perfect for enjoying morning coffee or evening sunsets. The oversized, detached 40 X 28 garage offers ample storage space and protection for your vehicles from the elements as well as a large additional room in the back perfect for storage, worksop or entertaining. The 2-bedroom apartment above the garage is a fantastic bonus feature, whether for extended family or generating rental income.
